name: The Confidence of Fragility
description: The Confidence of Fragility recognizes the strength and courage required for those who face oppression and discrimination and acts as a reminder to everyone that inequality in any form, should not and cannot be tolerated. It is also an important acknowledgement of the enduring capacity for people to heal from the wounds of prejudice.  Collaboration by @dehiscenceart (collage) and @Namakubi_NFT (colour edits, audio, animation) 1080px, 12 sec MP4 with audio 32.9 mb 2021.
